cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper deals with crafting adversarial examples for machine learning classifiers, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the discretization problem, which is a concern in cryptography and security (cs.CR), and proposes a black-box method for crafting adversarial images, which involves optimization algorithms (cs.AI, cs.DS).
